title: Laura Ingraham Accepts REALITY, Randy Quaid Not So Much 11.25.20
itunes:title: Laura Ingraham Accepts REALITY, Randy Quaid Not So Much 11.25.20
description:
In episode 767, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian and Scam Goddess Laci Mosley to discuss Roger Stone fueling the Georgia fire, Laura Ingraham giving up, the woman who was blocking the Biden administration transition, the Randy Quaid videos, rich people buying second passports, Trump's presidential library, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Roger Stone-Tied Group Claims Dems Are Framing Them As Republican Party Turncoats
  2. Glum Laura Ingraham Tells Fox Viewers It’s Done: ‘I’d Be Lying’ If I Said Trump Still Had A Chance
  3. Secret Service agents asked about transferring to Florida to guard Trump after he leaves office: report
  4. Under pressure, Trump appointee Emily Murphy approves transition in unusually personal letter to Biden
  5. The Honorable Joseph R. Biden, Jr.
  6. Trump Posts Series of Bewildering, Deranged Videos From Actor Randy Quaid — And a Call to ‘Re-Vote’ the 2020 Election
  7. Rich Americans Are Increasingly Looking for Second Passport
  8. NBC News Historian Asks Where Trump’s Library Should Go, and Twitter Explodes with Suggestions
  9. The New ‘Donald J. Trump Presidential Library’ Is Fake News For His Detractors To Love
  10. Trump’s presidential library will be a shrine to his ego
  11. The Nixon Library Has Finally Stopped Calling Watergate a 'Coup'
  12. Presidential Libraries Are a Scam. Could Obama Change That?
  13. WATCH: Diamond Cafe - What I Want The Most (Official Video)
